  "title" : "How big is the chance to get a Java UUID.randomUUID collision?",
  "body" : "<p>I need to create some uniques files in Java and i plan to use UUID.randomUUID to generate their names. Is there any chance to get a collision for this? Should i do something like bellow os I shouldn't worry about this?</p>\n\n<pre><code>Integer attemptsToGenerateUUID = 1;\n\nwhile (true) {\n    UUID fileUUID = UUID.randomUUID();\n\n    if (fileDoesNotExistwith this UUID name) {\n        save file;\n        break;\n    }\n\n    attemptsToGenerateUUID += 1;\n\n    if (attemptsToGenerateUUID &gt; 64) {\n        return false;\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
